Parliament, Wednesday, 6 March 2019 – A joint meeting of the Standing and Select Committees on Appropriations will tomorrow be briefed by National Treasury on the 2019 Division of Revenue Bill, as well as the 2019 Public Audit Excess Fee Bill. Details of the meeting are as follows: Date: Thursday, 7 March 2019
	Time: 12.30 pm
	Venue: Committee Room E249, Second Floor, National Assembly Building ISSUED BY THE PARLIAMENTARY COMMUNICATION SERVICES ON BEHALF OF THE CHAIRPERSONS OF THE STANDING AND SELECT COMMITTEES ON APPROPRIATIONS, MS YVONNE PHOSA AND MR CHAREL DE BEER. For media enquiries or interviews with the Chairpersons, please contact: Name: Felicia Lombard
	Parliamentary Communication Services
	Tel: 021 403 8285
	Cell: 081 548 7011
	E-mail: flombard@parliament.gov.za The word “Parliament” comes from the French word “parler” which means “to speak”.Read more